{
  "texts": [
    "We ran GPT-4 via a secure Azure PHI-compliant instance.",
    "The other five models were run on a PHI-compliant virtual machine with 4xNVIDIA A100 80GB GPUs.",
    "We designed prompts that included synthetic in-context examples generated by GPT-4 78.",
    "We included five examples for each entity, covering all possible labels that the LLM was to discern: \"0\" for entity negated/absence, \"1\" for presence, and \"2\" for uncertainty.",
    "We selected 5-shot prompting based on its demonstrated performance gains in prior work 36."
  ]
}